<L>__{exterior garage morning}
<A>__{turning a corner, riley and charlie stop in front of a rundown garage with a tarp hanging down instead of a door. riley pulls it aside and looks in. a hobo lies asleep on a grease stained floor, curled under some old newspapers.}
<C>__{riley}
<D>__{where's the car?}
<C>__{obo}
<P>__{(waking) what car?}
